> **Purpose:** Configuration and routing for Cursor AI sessions.
> Read this first, then follow the routing table to `docs/`.

## Project Overview

**Context_Map** is an agent-first repository template and guide. It demonstrates
the patterns it teaches. `docs/` is the system of record. All agent entry files
are routing tables — they point to docs, they never duplicate content.

